{"type": "article", "id": 50722, "title": "经常出国，你需要一个小而美的电源适配器｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-01T23:12:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48132, "name": "Momocca"}, {"id": 18311, "name": "Native Union"}, {"id": 48133, "name": "New Works"}, {"id": 2629, "name": "HAY"}, {"id": 18827, "name": "Sebastian Bergne"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 182, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180302000011WIvcPDrp6kNVJg8u.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #4d4d4d; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #4d4d4d} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s8 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s9 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #4d4d4d; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #4d4d4d} span.s10 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Result Chair &amp; Pyramid Collection by Friso Kramer &amp; Wim Rietveld for HAY</h3><p>Result 椅和 Pyramid 系列是由 Friso Kramer 和 Wim Rietveld 于 1950 年代末期设计的，当时两位设计师在 Ahrend 工作。以灵活、轻便、结实为特性，该系列产品主要为 1960-1970 年代荷兰的学校生产制作。并且自从他们诞生以来就一直被广泛使用至今。</p><p>最近，丹麦设计品牌 HAY 与 Ahrend 合作，重新量产了 Result 椅和 Pyramid 系列。它结构极简，足够轻巧，易于搬运。经典的设计表现出卓越功能和美观轻盈，已在几代人的实际使用环境中得到佐证。切割钢板椅架有黑色和深灰色喷漆两款，配橡木或烟熏橡木椅座，椅背或桌面。Pyramid Collection 有几款不同的设计结构，包括桌子、书桌、长凳，他们简洁的椅架使人一目了然几款产品的关联性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000038wzfnZlmaRBEP9L2N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000040Ezwj04yXmsOrAJqh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.209167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000039YVTcwo3nbqlLy6ka.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803020000390IvGB7ERzdoPTxZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803020000406ew1o975fR0svHPr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://hay.dk/ms-my/sections/series/pyramid-and-result\" rel=\"nofollow\">HAY</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Latest Collection by New Works</h3><p>总部设在哥本哈根的设计公司 New Works 最近在 2018 nian 斯德哥尔摩家具展上展出了他们的最新系列。基于自然、实验、未经加工的以及手工艺四大核心价值观，这个系列作品可以说是功能设计和雕塑艺术之间的结合产物，包括灯具、家具以及装饰品。每件作品都提供各种饰面和颜色选择，将其放在一起时，可以无缝融合在一起使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000133ebzmy70wDYfJ4CpN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.865625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000133q6Jkxt1gPZEMCfXb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000133KkIcESOoCBuUvtp6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000134cJu9EASsFzlkibNn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000134GAIiaMCbpPOur0ng.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000134or69TImSE1PZWOu8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000135Aw6atbIcDkGOrHvZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.newworks.dk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">New Works</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Smart Charger International by Native Union</h3><p>对于频繁往返于国内外出差的人，有个烦恼可能是大多数酒店都缺乏兼容的电源插座。经验丰富的人都会随身携带一个电源适配器和便携式充电器，但大多数适配器都尺寸很大且设计不佳。</p><p>Native Union 是香港一家配件品牌，擅长处理美学和功能性的平衡。 Smart Charger International 是其解决这一难题的一个精简、摩登的解决方案，提供 4 个 USB 端口，配有 A、C 和 G 型电源适配器插头，兼容美国、加拿大、欧洲等国最常见的电源插座。售价 34.99 美元，<a href=\"https://www.nativeunion.com/smart-charger-international/?utm_source=RAN&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2454844&amp;ranMID=42662&amp;ranEAID=je6NUbpObpQ&amp;ranSiteID=je6NUbpObpQ-N16SCWOMuBQcCcfAFaG8FA\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803020002358wHoTbs4nNGJeZRC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664844\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018030200023418ctIX3vpkCJFydD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000235BzCqDewH2p16ukS3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000235XPyn2RuUSi3gqQpa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000236x0jruq1pfCnGPY6B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.459559\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Adara by Momocca </h3><p>西班牙家具公司 Momocca 推出了一系列存储类家具，将木材、金属和石材结合起来，呈现出大胆而简约的外观。这个系列名为 Adara ，包括餐具柜、抽屉柜等，饰面以及台面的材料都可以根据用户的喜好进行定制，用户甚至可以选择不同模块堆叠、组合的方式，或是为柜子添加不同高度的柜腿。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000305Mb1txBm9OPKdlsV8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000305c7nApB3O190lfIvt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803020003056nSk1jrCZmu8Kavt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000305bPtchRfq6eGWKyUM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000305QRm2awCZO0BIuKU9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000305SdrvN1DlB2ejxV5n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000306dZPHGRrMQBIg10VF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.momocca.com/my-product_category/coleccion-adara/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">Momocca</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Poise lamps by Sebastian Bergne</h3><p>Poise 灯具最近在纽约野口勇博物馆的 Akari Unfolded 展览中展出，设计师是 Sebastian Bergne。Poise 灯具以艺术家野口勇简洁质朴的作品为灵感来源，利用纸、铅、绳索和不锈钢等多种材料，创造出一项有着微妙平衡感的艺术作品。柔和的灯光令人联想到摄影工作室的场景。</p><p>Poise 通过一种常见于纸袋的折叠手法，被转变为介于实用设计与雕塑之间的作品，呼应了野口勇一贯的跨学科式的创新作风。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000346JutWIseUZ1X9jcxa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.775000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000346iABH7JCukM0Uw5fp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000346OfLpXqNV9yHsugdE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000345d2857yMlj0wqbWXp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000346aszc0bxF4BD6qMGY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000346YKUqDB9Lxd3Wj0r4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.613542\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Aromax Scent Diffuser</h3><p>家是能够给予很多人最高舒适度和安全感的空间，设计师认为，在家中有必要创造一种氛围，激发我们的感官。Aromax 是一款极简主义扩香器，灵感来自其家庭和个人体验的回忆。</p><p>Aromax 采用阳极氧化铝制成的圆锥状造型，很雅致。内部设有一个可以更安静地分散芳香剂的装置，还可以调节扩香强度。此外，Aromax 还有十款 30 毫升的手工制作的精油，比如无花果、柠檬香草茶以及雪松等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000418VoWxpKzgLN9cXn2J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.999375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000419tg8K4vSRm0fUyPz6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000419BOWzbcLNduFkMmtw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000419LvnpyEs8FZW0RSNO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000419P2qivNzjsAVlwmh7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180302000420qFP2vRp1hxkQlbV5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.498589\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}